00:00:07,070 --> 00:00:10,400
今日はやけに目が疼く

2
00:00:07,230 --> 00:00:10,440
My eyes are throbbing with pain
more than usual today.

3
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:12,950
侵入者

4
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,820
Intruders?

5
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:16,450
A small and weak female voice.

6
00:00:16,820 --> 00:00:19,070
地下に閉じ込める気だ

7
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:18,870
They intend to trap her underground.

8
00:00:19,070 --> 00:00:20,440
ダメだ

9
00:00:19,410 --> 00:00:20,200
They mustn't.

10
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:32,600
四龍の戦士よ

11
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:32,630
Warriors of the four dragons...

12
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,820
なんだ

13
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:33,510
What is this?

14
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:38,090
これより お前達は我々の分身

15
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:37,890
You are now our other halves.

16
00:00:38,580 --> 00:00:46,570
緋龍を主とし 命の限り これを守り
これを愛し 決して裏切るな

17
00:00:38,680 --> 00:00:43,390
You will serve Hiryuu as your master, protecting him with your lives.

18
00:00:43,390 --> 00:00:46,690
You will love him and never betray him.

19
00:00:46,570 --> 00:00:48,630
なんだ この声は

20
00:00:46,690 --> 00:00:48,650
What is this voice?

21
00:01:00,020 --> 00:01:01,650
目が疼く

22
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,870
My eyes are throbbing.

23
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:07,930
あの少女に触れた時 声が響いて

24
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:07,960
The moment I touched that girl,
a voice echoed through my head.

25
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:11,800
その場に崩れ落ちてしまいそうになった

26
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:11,880
I nearly collapsed where I stood.

27
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:16,170
白い龍が居た

28
00:01:13,670 --> 00:01:16,180
There was a white dragon.

29
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:21,030
どうして俺は 彼を白い龍だと思ってあんだろう

30
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:21,350
Why did I think he was a white dragon?

31
00:01:22,020 --> 00:01:23,980
どうしてこんなに...

32
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:24,020
Why does it feel...

33
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:27,690
血が炊けるように熱い

34
00:01:24,810 --> 00:01:27,600
like my blood is boiling?

35
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,360
My eyes are throbbing.

36
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:30,420
目が疼く

37
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:32,530
Be still.

38
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:32,800
静まれ

39
00:01:33,470 --> 00:01:38,430
この力はもう二度と知られてはならないのだから

40
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:38,570
No one must learn of this power again.

