737
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:23,740
That's ridiculous!

738
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:28,370
The four dragon warriors must hasten to join their master immediately.

739
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:28,440
四龍たるもの 主の元に一刻も早くはせ参じるものだ

740
00:04:28,370 --> 00:04:32,750
